{
	"description": "Shift is a wall lamp with impressive luminous power. Designed by Marco Piva, it redefines the concept of a wall lamp, integrating with spaces in perfect harmony: compact and discreet, its neutral finishes further enhance its ability to blend into its surroundings, almost disappearing to allow the light to take centre stage, fostering and enriching its interplay with the space.\nThe understated, minimalist design draws on the clean, rigorous lines of contemporary architecture, softened by subtly rounded corners. The entirely black internal structure enhances the power of the light beam – exceeding 5,000 lm in the Large version – and ensures uniform light distribution and high quality, while the LED source is strategically positioned to amplify the luminous effect and prevent unwanted shadows on the walls.\n\nCrafted from aluminium, Shift is available in two sizes – Small and Large – and four sophisticated finishes: matte black, matte white, extra-matte champagne, and the new natural brown. These finishes are designed to complement various settings while accentuating the lamp’s clean and essential lines. Shift is equipped with two interchangeable screens that adjust the light’s perception and angle: it comes pre-assembled with a transparent screen, which can be easily replaced with a sandblasted screen to create a more diffused wall effect and reduce light projection onto the ceiling.\n\nThanks to its high luminous output, Shift can effectively illuminate medium-sized spaces on its own. From hotel bedrooms to residential living areas, it creates captivating interactions between light and space, offering high-performance lighting solutions with a sophisticated yet understated presence. Shift is also ideal for stairwells and corridors, where it can be installed in sequences, as well as in rooms with low ceilings or exposed beams that deserve to be highlighted.\n\nThe lamp is available with both DALI and TRIAC drivers, ensuring greater flexibility to suit various needs.",
